# Discord User Token
# ⚠️  WARNING: User tokens violate Discord TOS for automation. Use at your own risk.
# How to get your user token:
#   1. Open Discord in browser (https://discord.com/app)
#   2. Open DevTools (F12) → Application tab
#   3. Local Storage → https://discord.com → find key "token"
#   4. Copy the value (remove surrounding quotes if any)
# For bot tokens: https://discord.com/developers/applications
DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=your_discord_user_token_or_bot_token_here

# JWT Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your-secure-random-string-at-least-32-characters-long
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=8h

# Password to access the web interface (change this!)
ACCESS_PASSWORD=your-secure-password
